*Konj* je zvao za trkom. (The *horse* was neighing for the race.)

*Konja* su čuvali u staji. (The *horses* were kept in the stable.)

Mladić je obukao *konjsku* opremu. (The young man put on *horse* gear.)

Dečak je često jahao *konja*. (The boy often rode the *horse*.)

Svi su se mnogo radovali *konju*. (Everyone was delighted with the *horse*.)